-- Contract rewards are paid by the bank when completion is confirmed.
-- MineColonies/courier delivery can now complete contracts automatically:
-- if a courier deposits any positive amount of a requested item, the order is
-- treated as fulfilled and the reward is paid to the warehouse/logistics company.
